<br>
As for monks, if monks didn't have FD at all...they would still be one of the best classes in the game.  Best solo melee and best xp group tank.  Monks would lose some power on raids, because they can't go full out damage and live due to FD hate blurring (which is different from mem blurring), and of course they wouldn't be good pullers - but then again, they were never intended to be a crowd control class at all.<br>
